# pymod

## installation

```shell
pip install pymod
```

## config

1. `.` (script directory)
2. ` ~/.config/pymod`
3. `/usr/local/etc/pymod`

## shell usage

- take advantage of command substitution

### bash

```shell
$(pymod -u ompi)
```

### fish

```shell
eval (pymod -u ompi)
```


